{"tid":536387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【齊齊奉獻】港珠澳大橋嚴重超支 澳門硬食近六億元","createTime":"2018-01-21T17:28:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-22T02:03:31.000Z","uid":43189,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6f4466c8a78504a23fb92082252eca372c117d26","tid":536387,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T17:28:45.000Z","msg":"即時報道<br />\n<br />\n文：論盡採訪組<br />\n<br />\n時間：2018年01月21日 17:17<br />\n<br />\n港珠澳大橋工程嚴重超支逾百億元人民幣。建設發展辦公室在回覆議員吳國昌書面質詢表示，港珠澳大橋主體工程合同價為381.18億元人民幣，其中三地政府共同承擔的金額為157.3億，其餘的建設費則透過貸款融資，按三地出資分攤比例，澳門佔12.59%，即19.8億，有關金額每年已按工程進度支付。<br />\n<br />\n另外，在主體工程的超支金額上，根據三地的協議，三地政府有責任對超支的46.88億按照出資比例作攤分，不論超支問題可否歸責澳門，特區政府也必須按協議承擔超支費用。以澳門佔比例12.59%計算，即需承擔5.9億元人民幣，該金額已於去年支付。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://aamacau.com/2018/01/21/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%B6%85%E6%94%AF-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%A1%AC%E9%A3%9F%E8%BF%91%E5%85%AD%E5%84%84%E5%85%83/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faamacau.com%2F2018%2F01%2F21%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%258F%25A0%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%25A9%258B%25E5%259A%25B4%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%2594%25AF-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%25A1%25AC%25E9%25A3%259F%25E8%25BF%2591%25E5%2585%25AD%25E5%2584%2584%25E5%2585%2583%2F&d=rompolGLBL1lnqJLfNhIbxFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=5d54c5f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://aamacau.com/2018/01/21/%E6%B8%AF%E7%8F%A0%E6%BE%B3%E5%A4%A7%E6%A9%8B%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E8%B6%85%E6%94%AF-%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%A1%AC%E9%A3%9F%E8%BF%91%E5%85%AD%E5%84%84%E5%85%83/</a>"},{"pid":"8e0bf648bb3f44fda1ec251e1e3e16b5a773486e","tid":536387,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T17:34:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾橋 <br />\n睇死起完都唔用得"},{"pid":"5043f5c8bbabd126af0d6f72393457d8913da3b0","tid":536387,"uid":53026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e0bf648bb3f44fda1ec251e1e3e16b5a773486e","tid":536387,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0